sequenceDiagram
    participant Main
    participant Entrees
    participant Vegetables
    participant Sides
    participant TranState
    participant API as "API/Database"

    Main->>Entrees: Get entree options
    Entrees->>API: GET entrees data
    API-->>Entrees: Return entrees array
    Entrees-->>Main: Radio button event for entrees

    Main->>Vegetables: Get vegetable options
    Vegetables->>API: GET vegetables data
    API-->>Vegetables: Return vegetables array
    Vegetables-->>Main: Radio button event for veggies

    Main->>Sides: Get side options
    Sides->>API: GET sides data
    API-->>Sides: Return sides array
    Sides-->>Main: Radio button event for sides

    Note over Main, TranState: User clicks options
    Main->>TranState: Save entreeChoice / vegChoice / sideChoice

    Note over Main, TranState: User clicks "Purchase Combo"
    Main->>TranState: orderPlaced()
    TranState->>API: POST tState order
    API-->>TranState: Order saved
    TranState-->>Main: transmit "stateChanged"
    Main->>Main: Render page